# apiruns-cli

Apiruns CLI is a tool to make self-configurable rest API. Create an API rest has never been so easy.

## Requirements

- Python 3.6+

## Installation.

```bash
pip install apiruns
```

```bash
poetry install
```

## Example

```bash
apiruns --help

